---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Medical Practice Accounting — CA Accounting | Doctors, Dentists, Vets"
  description="Specialty accounting for medical practices: doctors, dentists, chiropractors, and veterinarians. Practice management, equipment depreciation, multi-entity structures, and physician retirement planning."
>
  <section class="bg-cream-warm py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 fade-in">Industries · Medical Practices</p>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-navy leading-tight mb-6 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          The accounting work behind a working practice.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-charcoal text-lg leading-relaxed fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
          We work with practicing doctors, dentists, chiropractors, veterinarians, and other licensed professionals — the people who'd rather see patients than reconcile statements. Our role is to handle the financial infrastructure so the practice runs cleanly and the partners actually keep what they earn.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-16">
        <div class="lg:col-span-1 fade-in">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-4">What we handle</h2>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
            Medical practices have specific financial complexities — equipment, partners, retirement plans, and structuring across multiple entities. We've built our medical practice work around all of them.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Practice management</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Bookkeeping, payroll, AR aging analysis, and monthly financials structured for medical practices, not generic small businesses.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Equipment depreciation</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Section 179, bonus depreciation under Section 168(k), and cost segregation strategies for capital equipment, imaging, and chair financing.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Multi-entity structures</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">PC, PLLC, real estate holding entities, and management companies — designed to protect assets and optimize tax treatment.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Physician retirement planning</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Defined benefit plans, cash balance plans, profit-sharing, and Solo 401(k) strategies for high-earning practitioners.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Partner buy-in & buy-out</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Valuations, structuring, and tax-efficient mechanics for adding or transitioning practice partners.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Tax planning</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Year-round strategy across personal and practice returns, with quarterly check-ins to manage estimated payments and surprises.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-navy text-cream py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="fade-in">
          <p class="text-cream/60 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Who we work with</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-cream mb-6">
            Practitioners and the practices they run.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-cream/80 text-base leading-relaxed">
            Solo practitioners, partnerships, multi-location groups, and the management companies that support them. Whether you own one chair or five offices, the financial work scales with the practice.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-cream/70 text-sm fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Physicians & specialists</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Dentists & orthodontists</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Chiropractors</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Veterinarians</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Optometrists</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Surgical groups</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Multi-location practices</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Practice management companies</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-cream-warm py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-6">
          Talk to a CPA who knows the difference between Section 179 and a CPT code.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-10">
          The first conversation is free. We'll look at how the practice is structured today and tell you whether we can make it run more efficiently.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="btn-modern inline-block bg-forest text-cream font-semibold px-10 py-4 rounded hover:bg-forest-hover transition-colors"
        >
          Schedule a Free Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
